title: Railworks TS2014 Just Trains RR BR03
description:
Romantic Railroads shows the German Railways DRG Class BR03 Express Steam locomotive as it was in service in Germany during 1920-1945 and the Polish version when used from the late 1950s to 1968. Romantic Railroads includes different steam locomotives and tender variants, along with several passenger coaches of the Deutsche Reichsbahn and the PKP Railways in Poland.

This is the updated version which includes the rebuilt 03 of the Deutsche Reichsbahn from the 1970s (period IV). It is the 03 2228-9 which had 1000mm sized leading wheels.
